"title": "5955: strength, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5955: strength, divine",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The strength of God is made known in creation and redemption and in his empowering of believers to live faithfully.</p>\n<h2>The revelation of the strength of God</h2>\n<h3>In creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:4\">JOB 38:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:8\">JOB 38:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:12\">JOB 38:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:31-Job38:33\">JOB 38:31–38:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:34\">PSA 68:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:1-Ps104:3\">PSA 104:1–104:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:32\">PSA 104:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:12\">ISA 40:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:25-Isa40:26\">ISA 40:25–40:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:17\">JER 32:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2-Heb1:3\">HEB 1:2–1:3</a></p>\n<h3>In providence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:6\">PSA 135:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:8-Ps46:10\">PSA 46:8–46:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:3\">PSA 115:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:24\">ISA 14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:23\">ISA 40:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:5\">JER 27:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:35\">DAN 4:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26\">ACT 17:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11\">EPH 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>In redemption</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:6\">EXO 6:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:19-Eph1:20\">EPH 1:19–1:20</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:19-Exod3:20\">EXO 3:19–3:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:34\">DEU 4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:37\">DEU 4:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:13-Ps77:15\">PSA 77:13–77:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:10\">ISA 51:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:21\">JER 32:21</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:24\">DEU 3:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:2-2Sam22:3\">2SA 22:2–22:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:1-Ps18:2\">PSA 18:1–18:2</a> <em>David's song of praise for deliverance</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:1\">PSA 98:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:1\">ISA 59:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:16\">ISA 59:16</a></p>\n<h3>In human weakness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:9-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:9–12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:4\">2CO 13:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:4-Judg7:7\">JDG 7:4–7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:25-1Cor1:27\">1CO 1:25–1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:34\">HEB 11:34</a></p>\n<h3>In judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:15-Rev6:17\">REV 6:15–6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:10\">PSA 89:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:5-Isa63:6\">ISA 63:5–63:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:33-Ezek20:35\">EZK 20:33–20:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:12\">HAB 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8-2Thess1:9\">2TH 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:7\">2PE 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:12-Rev6:14\">REV 6:12–6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:8\">REV 18:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's strength brings comfort to believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:1\">PSA 27:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:3\">PSA 27:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28-John10:29\">JHN 10:28–10:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:31\">ROM 8:31</a></p>",
